						<div class="post-header">
							<h1 class="title entry-title">After work, relax like a Vigneron&#8230; with Wine</h1>

							<!-- BEGIN .post-meta-info -->
							<div class="post-meta-info">
								<span class="blog-author minor-meta">
																		<span class="post-date date updated">Feb 6, 2015</span>
																		
																		<span class="text-sep">|</span>
									
																		Posted by									<span class="entry-author-link" itemprop="name">
										<span class="vcard author">
											<span class="fn">
												<a href="http://socialvignerons.com/author/julienmiquel/" title="Posts by Julien Miquel" rel="author">Julien Miquel</a>
											</span>
										</span>
									</span>
																	</span>
																<span class="text-sep">|</span>
								
																	<!-- Category info -->
									<span class="blog-categories minor-meta"> 
																			<a href="http://socialvignerons.com/category/blog/" title="View all posts in Blog">Blog</a>, 			
																			<a href="http://socialvignerons.com/category/blog/wine-and-fun/" title="View all posts in Wine &amp; Fun">Wine &amp; Fun</a>, 			
																			<a href="http://socialvignerons.com/category/blog/wine-porn/" title="View all posts in Wine Porn">Wine Porn</a>			
																		<span class="text-sep">|</span>
								
															</div>
							<!-- END .post-meta-info -->

						</div>
						<!-- END .post-header -->
												
												<!-- BEGIN .entry-content -->
						<div class="entry-content clearfix" itemprop="text">
							<script><!--
dynamicgoogletags.update();
//--></script><p style="text-align: justify;">Vignerons (wine growers) work hard to make their passion turn into the best possible wine, for our own delight.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">They know better than anyone how a nice glass of wine after a hard day&#8217;s work is one of the <strong>most simple and pleasurable moments in life&#8230;</strong></p>
<div id="attachment_795" style="width: 1150px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="http://i0.wp.com/socialvignerons.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/Time-Life-France-vineyard1.jpg"><img class="wp-image-795 size-full" src="http://i0.wp.com/socialvignerons.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/Time-Life-France-vineyard1.jpg?resize=1140%2C1600" alt="Vigneron and glass of wine after harvest day" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a><p class="wp-caption-text">Vigneron and glass of wine after harvest</p></div>
<p style="text-align: justify;">I was a winemaker across the globe for many years. Believe me, it&#8217;s even better tasting your own production while working hard at harvest and making the next vintage&#8217;s wine.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">You&#8217;ve enjoyed this? Make sure you favorite, and check out more <a title="Wine Porn fun posts" href="http://socialvignerons.com/category/blog/wine-porn/">Wine Porn posts</a>.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
